date=2021-10-08|archive-date=2021-10-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211008211351/https://oglobo.globo.com/politica/psol-pede-cassacao-de-jaqueline-roriz-por-falta-de-decoro-parlamentar-2814575|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

