== 争议 ==

=== 开除Cabo Daciolo ===
2015年5月， 社会主义与自由党全国委员会开除联邦议员Cabo Daciolo，因为他提出[[宪法修正|宪法修正案]]12/2015，提议将宪法中规定“一切权力来自人民”的部分更改为“一切权力来自上帝”，这违背了PSOL主张的[[世俗国家|世俗国家]]。另外他还呼吁PSOL为[[Rocinha贫民窟|Rocinha贫民窟]]的治安警察部队辩护，该警队被指控在2013年6月杀害瓦匠学徒Caso Amarildo。开除Cabo Daciolo的决定以54票对1票通过<ref>{{Cite web|language=pt-br|title=PSOL expulsa deputado Daciolo por desacordo com estatuto e programa partidário|url=https://agenciabrasil.ebc.com.br/politica/noticia/2015-05/psol-expulsa-deputado-daciolo-por-desacordo-com-estatuto-e-programa|date=17 de maio de 2015|publisher=EBC|access-date=2021-10-08|archive-date=2021-10-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211009011432/https://agenciabrasil.ebc.com.br/politica/noticia/2015-05/psol-expulsa-deputado-daciolo-por-desacordo-com-estatuto-e-programa|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 反犯罪一揽子法案 ===
2019年12月上旬，众议院全体会议批准紧急处理打击犯罪一揽子法案（PL 10372/18）。该法案以359票对9票通过。PSOL是唯一反对该法案的紧急性的政党<ref>{{Cite web|language=pt-br|title=Câmara aprova regime de urgência para pacote anticrime; só PSOL foi contra|url=https://exame.abril.com.br/brasil/camara-aprova-regime-de-urgencia-para-pacote-anticrime-so-psol-foi-contra/|work=Exame|publisher=Abril|access-date=2021-10-08|archive-date=2019-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191206172421/https://exame.abril.com.br/brasil/camara-aprova-regime-de-urgencia-para-pacote-anticrime-so-psol-foi-contra/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，反犯罪项目由当时的司法部长Sergio Moro起草<ref>{{Cite web|language=pt-br|title=Entenda o pacote anticrime aprovado na Câmara|url=https://g1.globo.com/politica/noticia/2019/12/05/entenda-o-projeto-anticrime-aprovado-na-camara.ghtml|date=5 de dezembro de 2019|work=G1|publisher=Globo|access-date=2021-10-08|archive-date=2021-10-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211008211413/https://g1.globo.com/politica/noticia/2019/12/05/entenda-o-projeto-anticrime-aprovado-na-camara.ghtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在听证会辩论二审监狱的宪法修正案后，Moro在推特上质疑：“我不喜欢这种政治游戏。但事实需要被告知。在反犯罪法案中，我们提议明确将民兵定性为犯罪组织。我们还提出了其他几项打击有组织犯罪的措施。 PSOL的Freixo/Glauber 反对所有这些”<ref>{{Cite web|language=pt-br|title=Após discussão, Sergio Moro questiona PSOL por oposição a projeto anticrime|url=https://www.bol.uol.com.br/noticias/2020/02/13/apos-discussao-sergio-moro-questiona-psol-por-oposicao-a-projeto-anticrime.htm|publisher=Uol|access-date=2021-10-08|archive-date=2021-10-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211008211348/https://www.bol.uol.com.br/noticias/2020/02/13/apos-discussao-sergio-moro-questiona-psol-por-oposicao-a-projeto-anticrime.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== Leonel Brizola Neto致敬金正恩 ===
2019 年12月12日，已故州长Leonel Brizola的孙子、当时的市议员Leonel Brizola Neto（PSOL，里约热内卢州）向[[朝鲜民主主义人民共和国|朝鲜]]领导人[[金正恩|金正恩]]公开致敬，引起党内反弹。 11月29日，他在里约热内卢市议会向金正恩提交了一份“表扬和表彰议案”，据《环球报》报道。该行为受到里约市PSOL党部的谴责，党部发表声明称不支持这个提案，是Brizola Neto个人的行为，该动议“不值得支持或投票”<ref>{{Cite web|language=pt-br|title=Vereador homenageia Kim Jong-un e gera polêmica no PSOL|url=https://noticias.r7.com/politica/vereador-homenageia-kim-jong-un-e-gera-polemica-no-psol-12122019|access-date=16 de maio de 2020|date=12 de dezembro de 2019|publisher=R7|archive-date=2021-10-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211008211351/https://noticias.r7.com/politica/vereador-homenageia-kim-jong-un-e-gera-polemica-no-psol-12122019|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|language=pt-br|title=Deputado do Psol homenageia Kim Jong-un na Assembleia do RJ|url=https://congressoemfoco.uol.com.br/mundo-cat/deputado-do-psol-homenageia-kim-jong-un-na-assembleia-do-rj/|access-date=16 de maio de 2020|publisher=Congresso em Foco|archive-date=2021-04-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210420215657/https://congressoemfoco.uol.com.br/mundo-cat/deputado-do-psol-homenageia-kim-jong-un-na-assembleia-do-rj/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|language=pt-br|title=Vereador do PSOL do RJ homenageia Coreia do Norte e Kim Jong-un|url=https://www.metropoles.com/brasil/politica-brasil/vereador-do-psol-do-rj-homenageia-coreia-do-norte-e-kim-jong-un|access-date=16 de maio de 2020|publisher=Metropoles}}</ref>。
